member.summary:
Multi-purpose cache for tracking data at a grid position.
- Mount point position caching (check if there is any valid mount point given the preview block is placed there)
- Grid overlap position caching (check if there is any overlapping blocks given the preview block is placed there)
- Grid storage caching (skipping storage checks by caching previous querys for a given position)
Automatically handles cache invalidation when the grid is modified or killed. Because the cache is multi-purpose, it is completely invalidated when modified.
